<div class="hero-main">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Disfruta tu<br />empresa</h1>
    <p>
      Diseñamos la esencia visual y estratégica de tu marca para que destaque
      donde realmente importa.
    </p>
    <button class="hero-btn">Contactar</button>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-dots">
    <span class="dot active"></span>
    <span class="dot"></span>
    <span class="dot"></span>
    <span class="dot"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .hero-main {
    background: #18181b;
    border-radius: 32px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 48px 32px 32px 32px;
    min-height: 420px;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 32px #0003;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .hero-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .hero-content h1 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .hero-content p {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .hero-btn {
    background: #fff;
    color: #18181b;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 0.7rem 2.2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition:
      background 0.2s,
      color 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #0002;
  }
  .hero-btn:hover {
    background: #e6e6e6;
  }
  .hero-dots {
    position: absolute;
    right: 32px;
    bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .dot {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    background: #fff;
    opacity: 0.5;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .dot.active {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .hero-main {
      max-width: 98vw;
      padding: 32px 8px 32px 8px;
      min-height: 320px;
    }
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.1rem;
    }
    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-dots {
      right: 16px;
      bottom: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>
